description: The Tinley Beverage Company Inc. manufactures and sells liquor-inspired, non-alcoholic, and cannabis-infused beverages. It offers Tinley Tonics and Tinley 27 infused beverages through retail locations, as well as online in California, United States. The company was formerly known as Quia Resources Inc. and changed its name to The Tinley Beverage Company Inc. in October 2015. The Tinley Beverage Company Inc. was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Toronto, Canada.
